title: Walt Disney - The Legend of Sleepy Hollow.avi
description:
This is a DVD-Rip of the original Walt Disney animation of The Legend of Sleepy Hollow narrated by Bing Crosby.

Note: The first part of the DVD, The Wind in the Willows featuring Mr. Toad was not ripped. 

*** This is not the 1999 film Sleepy Hollow starring Johnny Depp. ***

Enjoy! It&#039;s one of the many lost Walt Disney classics that aren&#039;t played on The Disney Channel anymore.
